# Coriolis Space Station
# Exported from DeepspaceOutpost ship data (SHIP id 2).
# Modified: flat docking marker replaced with a recessed open docking bay.
# Front +Z face rebuilt as a frame around a rectangular opening (verts 13-16),
# extruded inward 90 units (back wall at z=70) with interior walls + back wall.
